# Copy to `.forbidden-identifiers.txt` (gitignored) and add your real
# company/user/project names — one POSIX-extended regex per line. The
# check_no_identifiers pre-commit hook blocks any commit that reintroduces them,
# keeping a fork's published code free of internal identifiers.
#
# Examples (replace with your own):
# mycompany
# internal-project-[a-z]+
# \bjdoe\b
# @mycompany\.example
